  "content": "<p>很可能并不影响人类的进化。</p><p>因为灵长类在哺乳类中，恰好是基本没沾恐龙灭绝一点光的一支，恐龙灭绝后也混的跟在恐龙时代一样惨。</p><p>甚至比在恐龙时代还惨更惨，灵长类是在5000多万年前被啮齿类赶上树的。。。。。</p><p>在新生代大多数时间里，过去恐龙怎么欺负灵长类，哺乳类亲戚们就怎么欺负。。。。。</p><p>别以为哺乳类翻身了，灵长类就也翻身了:</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-bc67ca5a712b3d3f52a4c3de66c9a702_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-rawwidth=\"571\" data-rawheight=\"394\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-f2c612c64530a2536521c254c408c21c_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"571\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-bc67ca5a712b3d3f52a4c3de66c9a702_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;571&#39; height=&#39;394&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"571\" data-rawheight=\"394\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-f2c612c64530a2536521c254c408c21c_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"571\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-bc67ca5a712b3d3f52a4c3de66c9a702_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-bc67ca5a712b3d3f52a4c3de66c9a702_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\"/></figure><p>直到一群没有尾巴的猴子，被同类赶出了森林。。。。。。</p>",
